songs.title: They Know (Remix)
songs.lyrics:

I know I know I know

Just know that I know I know I know (Okay!)
Them streets, they fuck with me strong
And them bitches gon fuck just because money long

All I left her was my swisha wrapper nigga
I brought the rafe like a trapper nigga

Sittin in the traffic, you can smell dough
No tints for my niggas with the elbow
All glass in the watches that I wear now
All ass, older bitches that I care about
All cash in yo city then we tear up out it
Got that 308, don’t make me let that air up out it
Fuck around and make me knock yo dreads off
Shots fired, suspect speed off

I fucked yo bitch, she say you lame, I already know
Bvlgari shades on my face, I see no evil
I’m bout that Maybach Music shit, this is the sequel
Slab, time to turn up for these bitches come on
It’s 21, leaving with one of these bitches, I go to blue flame
I put that thing on these bitches so talkin KOD
I spend some change on them bitches and I know
Gotta forward the ex so I po
You say that’s yo bitch, nigga no that’s my hoe
But on Facebook my Rollie is gold
And I know I know I know
Slab
